reviewText: I love part 1,2,3 and 4 of Slug Street Scrappers. Plenty of comedy and action, people have different styles of fighting and there is no use of weapons or killing. I couldn't wait to watch it. Bobby  :-)
Great moovie , the best of Whirlwind Action Official !! The fighting choreography well , the pleasure to find Tess and Micah .

Slug street scrappers is a great series.  It has everything.  Comedy, action, drama, love story, even some magic.  The fight scenes are top notch done by highly skilled martial artists.  I definitely recommend this.  Its just a lot of fun to watch.
very cool,I like how this movie is a dedicaton to all the fighting video games .The martial arts in the movie is fantastic

Saw the first three of these in a marathon with some friends at our local gym. My kids loved them, and we all were laughing so hard it was a good thing we were mostly sitting on the mats... The dialogue and timing make eating/drinking an "at your own risk" activity when done at the same time, for sure. -AG
One of the best films I've seen in awhile. It has awesome fight scenes and witty banter.
One of the best independent action films I've ever seen!
